# Technology Stack

| Category | Technology | Notes |
|----------|-----------|-------|
| **Frontend** | React 19+ with TypeScript | Strict mode enabled |
| **Styling** | Tailwind CSS | Core utilities only |
| **Icons** | lucide-react | Consistent icon library |
| **Notifications** | React Toastify | Use toast functions, NOT alert() |
| **Maps** | Leaflet + react-leaflet | Map views and ride locations |
| **Backend** | AWS Amplify Gen 2 | Fully implemented |
| **Authentication** | AWS Amplify Auth (SSO) | Google + Apple Sign-In |
| **Data Storage** | AWS Amplify Data | GraphQL API with DynamoDB |
| **State Management** | React hooks | useState, useReducer, custom hooks |
| **Build Tool** | Vite | PWA support via vite-plugin-pwa |
| **Validation** | Zod | Form and data validation |
| **Testing** | Vitest (unit), Playwright (E2E) | See package.json scripts |

